            At Valley View School, Students in primary and secondary programs undertake a demanding curriculum intended to prepare them for pursing higher studies, which uniquely combines the curriculum in line of the government of Nepal and special learning experiences. Teachers are always at vigilance to help students during and after their class. The special learning experiences include varieties of activities to be pursued as per the individual choices.

